{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.1","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:1","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.059,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Galil\u00e9ens massacr\u00e9s par Pilate<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-5: cf. \u00c9z 18:30-32. Ro 2:3-6; 3:22, 23. Jn 8:24.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>En ce m\u00eame temps, quelques personnes qui se trouvaient l\u00e0 racontaient \u00e0 J\u00e9sus ce qui \u00e9tait arriv\u00e9 \u00e0 des Galil\u00e9ens dont Pilate avait m\u00eal\u00e9 le sang avec celui de leurs sacrifices.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.2","name":"Luc 13:2","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.59","name":"Luc 12:59","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.59"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.2","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:2","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il leur r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">Croyez-vous que ces Galil\u00e9ens fussent de plus grands p\u00e9cheurs que tous les autres Galil\u00e9ens, parce qu\u2019ils ont souffert de la sorte?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.3","name":"Luc 13:3","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.1","name":"Luc 13:1","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.3","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:3","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Non, je vous le dis. Mais si vous ne vous repentez, vous p\u00e9rirez tous \u00e9galement.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.4","name":"Luc 13:4","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.2","name":"Luc 13:2","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.4","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:4","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ou bien, ces dix-huit personnes sur qui est tomb\u00e9e la tour de Silo\u00e9 et qu\u2019elle a tu\u00e9es, croyez-vous qu\u2019elles fussent plus coupables que tous les autres habitants de J\u00e9rusalem?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.5","name":"Luc 13:5","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.3","name":"Luc 13:3","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.5","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:5","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Non, je vous le dis. Mais si vous ne vous repentez, vous p\u00e9rirez tous \u00e9galement.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.6","name":"Luc 13:6","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.4","name":"Luc 13:4","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.6","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:6","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.007,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Parabole du figuier st\u00e9rile<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 6-9: cf. \u00c9s 5:1-7. Mt 21:18, 19, 43. Ro 2:4, 5.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Il dit aussi cette parabole: <span class=\"wj\">Un homme avait un figuier plant\u00e9 dans sa vigne. Il vint pour y chercher du fruit, et il n\u2019en trouva point.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.7","name":"Luc 13:7","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.5","name":"Luc 13:5","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.7","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:7","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Alors il dit au vigneron: Voil\u00e0 trois ans que je viens chercher du fruit \u00e0 ce figuier, et je n\u2019en trouve point. Coupe-le: pourquoi occupe-t-il la terre inutilement?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.8","name":"Luc 13:8","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.6","name":"Luc 13:6","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.8","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:8","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Le vigneron lui r\u00e9pondit: Seigneur, laisse-le encore cette ann\u00e9e; je creuserai tout autour, et j\u2019y mettrai du fumier.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.9","name":"Luc 13:9","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.7","name":"Luc 13:7","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.9","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:9","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Peut-\u00eatre \u00e0 l\u2019avenir donnera-t-il du fruit; sinon, tu le couperas.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.10","name":"Luc 13:10","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.8","name":"Luc 13:8","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.10","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:10","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.011,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Gu\u00e9rison d\u2019une femme le jour du sabbat<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 10-17: cf. (Mt 12:9-13. Lu 14:1-6.) Ps 146:8.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>J\u00e9sus enseignait dans une des synagogues, le jour du sabbat.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.11","name":"Luc 13:11","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.9","name":"Luc 13:9","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.11","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:11","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Et voici, il y avait l\u00e0 une femme poss\u00e9d\u00e9e d\u2019un esprit qui la rendait infirme depuis dix-huit ans; elle \u00e9tait courb\u00e9e, et ne pouvait pas du tout se redresser.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.12","name":"Luc 13:12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.10","name":"Luc 13:10","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.12","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:12","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019il la vit, J\u00e9sus lui adressa la parole, et lui dit: <span class=\"wj\">Femme, tu es d\u00e9livr\u00e9e de ton infirmit\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.13","name":"Luc 13:13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.11","name":"Luc 13:11","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.13","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:13","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Et il lui imposa les mains. A l\u2019instant elle se redressa, et glorifia Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.14","name":"Luc 13:14","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.12","name":"Luc 13:12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.14","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:14","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Mais le chef de la synagogue, indign\u00e9 de ce que J\u00e9sus avait op\u00e9r\u00e9 cette gu\u00e9rison un jour de sabbat, dit \u00e0 la foule: Il y a six jours pour travailler; venez donc vous faire gu\u00e9rir ces jours-l\u00e0, et non pas le jour du sabbat.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.15","name":"Luc 13:15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.13","name":"Luc 13:13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.15","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:15","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Hypocrites!<\/span> lui r\u00e9pondit le Seigneur, <span class=\"wj\">est-ce que chacun de vous, le jour du sabbat, ne d\u00e9tache pas de la cr\u00e8che son b\u0153uf ou son \u00e2ne, pour le mener boire?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.16","name":"Luc 13:16","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.14","name":"Luc 13:14","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.16","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:16","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et cette femme, qui est une fille d\u2019Abraham, et que Satan tenait li\u00e9e depuis dix-huit ans, ne fallait-il pas la d\u00e9livrer de cette cha\u00eene le jour du sabbat?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.17","name":"Luc 13:17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.15","name":"Luc 13:15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.17","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:17","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Tandis qu\u2019il parlait ainsi, tous ses adversaires \u00e9taient confus, et la foule se r\u00e9jouissait de toutes les choses glorieuses qu\u2019il faisait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.18","name":"Luc 13:18","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.16","name":"Luc 13:16","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.18","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:18","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.019,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Paraboles du grain de s\u00e9nev\u00e9, et du levain<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 18-21: cf. (Mt 13:31-33. Mc 4:30-32.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>\n    Il dit encore: <span class=\"wj\">A quoi le royaume de Dieu est-il semblable, et \u00e0 quoi le comparerai-je?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.19","name":"Luc 13:19","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.17","name":"Luc 13:17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.19","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:19","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il est semblable \u00e0 un grain de s\u00e9nev\u00e9 qu\u2019un homme a pris et jet\u00e9 dans son jardin; il pousse, devient un arbre, et les oiseaux du ciel habitent dans ses branches.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.20","name":"Luc 13:20","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.18","name":"Luc 13:18","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.20","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:20","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Il dit encore: <span class=\"wj\">A quoi comparerai-je le royaume de Dieu?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.21","name":"Luc 13:21","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.19","name":"Luc 13:19","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.21","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:21","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il est semblable \u00e0 du levain qu\u2019une femme a pris et mis dans trois mesures de farine, pour faire lever toute la p\u00e2te.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.22","name":"Luc 13:22","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.20","name":"Luc 13:20","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.22","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:22","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.023,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La porte \u00e9troite<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 22-30: cf. (Mt 7:13, 14, 21-23; 8:11, 12; 19:30.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>\n    J\u00e9sus traversait les villes et les villages, enseignant, et faisant route vers J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.23","name":"Luc 13:23","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.21","name":"Luc 13:21","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.23","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:23","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Quelqu\u2019un lui dit: Seigneur, n\u2019y a-t-il que peu de gens qui soient sauv\u00e9s? Il leur r\u00e9pondit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.24","name":"Luc 13:24","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.22","name":"Luc 13:22","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.24","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:24","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Efforcez-vous d\u2019entrer par la porte \u00e9troite. Car, je vous le dis, beaucoup chercheront \u00e0 entrer, et ne le pourront pas.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.25","name":"Luc 13:25","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.23","name":"Luc 13:23","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.25","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:25","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Quand le ma\u00eetre de la maison se sera lev\u00e9 et<\/span><span class=\"wj\">aura ferm\u00e9 la porte, et que vous, \u00e9tant dehors, vous commencerez \u00e0 frapper \u00e0 la porte, en disant: Seigneur, Seigneur, ouvre-nous! Il vous r\u00e9pondra: Je ne sais<\/span><span class=\"wj\">d\u2019o\u00f9 vous \u00eates.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.26","name":"Luc 13:26","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.24","name":"Luc 13:24","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.26","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:26","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Alors vous vous mettrez \u00e0 dire: Nous avons mang\u00e9 et bu devant toi, et tu as enseign\u00e9 dans nos rues.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.27","name":"Luc 13:27","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.25","name":"Luc 13:25","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.27","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:27","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et il r\u00e9pondra: Je vous le dis, je ne sais d\u2019o\u00f9 vous \u00eates;<\/span><span class=\"wj\">retirez-vous de moi, vous tous, ouvriers d\u2019iniquit\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.28","name":"Luc 13:28","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.26","name":"Luc 13:26","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.28","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:28","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">C\u2019est l\u00e0 qu\u2019il y aura des pleurs et des grincements de dents,<\/span><span class=\"wj\">quand vous verrez Abraham, Isaac et Jacob, et tous les proph\u00e8tes, dans le royaume de Dieu, et que vous serez jet\u00e9s dehors.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.29","name":"Luc 13:29","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.27","name":"Luc 13:27","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.29","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:29","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il en viendra de l\u2019orient et de l\u2019occident, du nord et du midi; et ils se mettront \u00e0 table dans le royaume de Dieu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.30","name":"Luc 13:30","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.28","name":"Luc 13:28","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.30","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:30","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et voici, il y en a des derniers qui seront les premiers, et des premiers qui seront les derniers.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.31","name":"Luc 13:31","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.29","name":"Luc 13:29","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.31","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:31","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.032,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Hostilit\u00e9 d\u2019H\u00e9rode. Crimes et ch\u00e2timent de J\u00e9rusalem<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 31-35: cf. (Mt 23:34-39. Lu 19:41-44.) J\u00e9 6:6-15, 27-30.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Ce m\u00eame jour, quelques pharisiens vinrent lui dire: Va-t\u2019en, pars d\u2019ici, car H\u00e9rode veut te tuer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.32","name":"Luc 13:32","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.30","name":"Luc 13:30","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.32","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:32","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Il leur r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">Allez, et dites \u00e0 ce renard: Voici, je chasse les d\u00e9mons et je fais des gu\u00e9risons aujourd\u2019hui et demain, et le troisi\u00e8me jour j\u2019aurai fini.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.33","name":"Luc 13:33","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.31","name":"Luc 13:31","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.33","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:33","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais il faut que je marche aujourd\u2019hui, demain, et le jour suivant; car il ne convient pas qu\u2019un proph\u00e8te p\u00e9risse hors de J\u00e9rusalem.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.34","name":"Luc 13:34","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.32","name":"Luc 13:32","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.34","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:34","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">J\u00e9rusalem, J\u00e9rusalem, qui tues les proph\u00e8tes et qui lapides ceux qui te sont envoy\u00e9s,<\/span><span class=\"wj\">combien de fois ai-je voulu rassembler tes enfants, comme une poule rassemble sa couv\u00e9e sous ses ailes, et vous ne l\u2019avez pas voulu!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.35","name":"Luc 13:35","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.33","name":"Luc 13:33","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.35","label":"","reference":"Luc 13:35","prev_osis_id":"Luke.013.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.014.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.13.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Voici, votre maison vous sera laiss\u00e9e; mais, je vous le dis, vous ne me verrez plus, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que vous disiez:<\/span><span class=\"wj\">B\u00e9ni soit celui qui vient au nom du Seigneur!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.13","name":"Luc 13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.14.1","name":"Luc 14:1","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.14.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.34","name":"Luc 13:34","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc19ad9f5.36968878');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc19ad9f5.36968878\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc19ad9f5.36968878","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc19ad9f5.36968878'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc19ad9f5.36968878\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}